title: Israel’s Iron Dome IS Reagan’s Star Wars!
description: The CDC has sold out YOUR CHILDREN to the teachers unions, and we tell you how. Joe Biden had one of the most gaffetastic weeks of his presidency. We go over the highlights. Also, a comparison between Ronald Reagan and Donald Trump. And Tess Holliday claims she’s anorexic. Yes, THAT Tess Holliday. #CDC #Israel #TessHolliday
